12th Anniversary of the China Gold & Precious Metals Summit will be Held on Dec. 6-7, 2017 in Shanghai China  As China’s largest precious metals conference for knowledge sharing and partnership opportunities, China Gold &amp; Precious Metals Summit has gathered over 3500 senior executives from across the precious metals community and capital market including mining companies, refiners & fabricators, bullion dealers, mints, gold & commodity exchanges, investment &amp; bullion banks, central banks, trading houses, service providers as well as trade associations in the past 11 years. This year’s edition will definitely be your ideal platform to embrace cutting-edge technologies and solutions, meet your industry colleagues, showcase your services, seek new partners and explore more business opportunities. Just come to join us! Find more about this summit at http://www.chinagoldsummit.com